  "text": "The closest idea to the holistic schema matching is probably the recent REVERE proposal [CITATION_1] , which suggests to use a separately-built schema corpus as a \"knowledge-base\" for assisting matching of unseen sources. While sharing the same insights of statistical analysis over corpora, our approach differs in that it leverages input schemas themselves as the \"corpus.\"",
